  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide potable water to 4000 children in Cameroon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The problem of access to potable water has reached alarming proportions in Cameroon. Many chidren and women travel long distances to fetch water from doubtful sources thus exposing them to water borne related diseases like: diarrhoea, dysentery, cholera and skin diseases.Many persons especially children have lost their lives due to cholera outbreak. Some schools even had to close down due to the epidemic two years ago. We intend to provide clean water to  school children in 2012/2013.</narrative>
  </description>
